{
  "stem": "2830.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he kept in touch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After he sold everything there, I heard that he liquidated all his things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was already in-- oh, I went-- I went with my husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were four-- yeah-- we went-- I had to get out from Bergen-Belsen because there was no food, no future, and the winter was coming.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had no-- you know--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went-- They were already established in Bavaria, in Schwandorf.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His brother-- he was with his brother and three more friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Michael, and Abraham, and one more-- one was also my age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went with him, under the condition-- I'm going to find, you know, from the UNRRA-- you know, they give you-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to ORT to learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wanted, still, to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have pictures of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am a life member of ORT.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and, to school-- I went to school in Schwandorf, and I wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, then, I found-- there came a-- a letter to the Jewish Center in Schwandorf that the rabbi that so-and-so [NON-ENGLISH] is looking for a sister that old and that old.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, when we-- when I was with my husband, going already, in the American zone in Landsberg there, he recognized me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He told me that he saw my sister alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me that my sister's alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, I knew, but I didn't know where and when.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When that letter came to that rabbi-- that-- you know-- so I had already contacted then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I figured, dear God, I have somebody who's alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I didn't know where I'm going to wind up, still.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know-- want to wind up with-- with this.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
